# NEMETIC STRING
# Magna_Carta_Rebellion (C165)

Φ(Magna_Carta_Rebellion) = σ(law|resistance) ∘ ρ(authority|consent) ∘ λ(contract|rupture) ∘ β(legacy|interpretation) ∘ δγ(rights|enforcement) ∘ μ(charter|history) + ε | :dormant

# OPERATOR BREAKDOWN
# σ(law|resistance)          :: Air  :: Codification of resistance rights within law itself
# ρ(authority|consent)       :: Water :: Fluid relationship between governing power and consent of governed
# λ(contract|rupture)        :: Fire  :: Social contracts and their necessary rupture when trust breaks
# β(legacy|interpretation)   :: Wood  :: Organic growth of historical documents through reinterpretation
# δγ(rights|enforcement)     :: Earth :: Grounding tension between declared rights and practical enforcement
# μ(charter|history)         :: Metal :: Structural durability of written law against corrosive forces of time
